Boston-Marathon.comments: Started off too quickly and then struggled later on in the race. Need to work on race pacing. Suggest doing some Yasso 800m workouts.

London-Marathon.comments: Really enjoyed watching the elite mens set off. Managed to see Mo Farah. Going to have to take a few weeks rest after this race. My ankles are very soar from the London streets.

Chicago-Marathon.comments: Terrible race. Had the flu probably should have avoided starting this race. Lesson learnt.

Durham 100m Open.comments: Stumbled out of the blocks and then spend the race catching up. Another 10m and I would have got 1st.
